\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Custin 1.5 Turbo Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<\/td>\n<td>820 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<td>30 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Custin 1.5 Turbo \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t<\/td>\n<td>915 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<td>30 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Custin 2.0 Turbo Cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>974 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<td>25 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5 X\u0103ng Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<\/td>\n<td>979 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<td>50 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 Diesel Ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n<\/td>\n<td>1,070 t\u1ef7<\/td>\n<td>50 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.5 X\u0103ng Cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>1,160 t\u1ef7<\/td>\n<td>50 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Santa Fe 2.2 Diesel Cao c\u1ea5p<\/td>\n<td>1,219 t\u1ef7<\/td>\n<td>50 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Santa Fe Hybrid<\/td>\n<td>1,269 t\u1ef7<\/td>\n<td>100 tri\u1ec7u<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<h3>L\u1ec7 ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m theo<\/h3>\n<p>Vi\u1ec7c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n l\u1ebb khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu xe tr\u00ean gi\u1ea3m theo sau khi b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed9 T\u00e0i ch\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt. N\u1ebfu ph\u00ed tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m theo m\u1ee9c ni\u00eam y\u1ebft m\u1edbi, gi\u00e1 l\u0103n b\u00e1nh xe s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m th\u00eam \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Santa Fe c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfp 10-12 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng chi ph\u00ed l\u0103n b\u00e1nh.<\/p>\n<h3>Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n m\u1edbi t\u0103ng ph\u1ea7n c\u1ea1nh tranh so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7<\/h3>\n<p>Gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a 4 m\u1eabu xe Hyundai tr\u00ean tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea1nh tranh h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<\/p>\n<p>V\u00ed d\u1ee5 nh\u01b0 Hyundai Venue c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 kh\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u1ec9 499 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 519 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Kia Sonet. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu SUV h\u1ea1ng A ra m\u1eaft v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Xe c\u00f3 2 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n, d\u00f9ng chung \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 1.0L t\u0103ng \u00e1p c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 120 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 ly h\u1ee3p k\u00e9p 7 c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n<div class=\"mxhsingle2\"><\/div>\n<h2 class=\"sapo\">Xe Hyundai c\u00e0ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cao, m\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 ni\u00eam y\u1ebft c\u00e0ng nhi\u1ec1u. Khi gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh, kh\u00e1ch mua xe s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed l\u0103n b\u00e1nh.<\/h2>\n<div id=\"admzonek9yxbkb8\" class=\"pushed\">\n<div id=\"zone-k9yxbkb8\" class=\"pushed\">\n<div id=\"share-k9yxbkbl\">\n<div id=\"placement-k9yxcux2\">\n<div id=\"banner-k9yxbkb8-k9yxcuxk\">\n<div id=\"slot-1-k9yxbkb8-k9yxcuxk\">\n<div id=\"ssppagebid_5981\">\n<div id=\"adnzone_512565\" class=\"banner0\" data-ssp=\"sspbid_2014699\" data-admssprqid=\"318777b2-9fb5-4771-9649-d467a88ac3d9120-66714629\" data-location=\"7\" data-width=\"600\" data-height=\"90\">\n<div><\/div>\n<p><iframe id=\"adnzone_sponsor_512565\" scrolling=\"no\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"><\/iframe><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"content-id\" class=\"contentbody\">\n<div class=\"clearfix\"><\/div>\n<div data-check-position=\"autopro_detail_position_start\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"append_box_thread\" class=\"content-news-detail detail-content afcbc-body\" data-role=\"content\">\n<figure class=\"VCSortableInPreviewMode noCaption\">\n<div><a class=\"detail-img-lightbox\" title=\"\" href=\"https:\/\/autopro8.mediacdn.vn\/134505113543774208\/2024\/6\/18\/web-1718680993974189311194.jpg\" target=\"